<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé sū bǎo bèi 迦南35</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū bǎo bèi, bǎo bèi yé sū; yé sū ài wǒ, wǒ shǔ yé sū.
 wǒ zài xún qiú zhǔ de róng miàn, wǒ yǐ tīng jiàn zhǔ de shēng yīn;
 zhǔ shuō wǒ yǐ yǒng yuǎn de ài ài nǐ, wǒ de huà yǔ yǒng bù gǎi biàn,
 zhǐ yào nǐ zhēn xīn lái xún qiú wǒ de miàn, wǒ bì dìng ràng nǐ dé yǐ xún jiàn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>35</hymn_number>
</song>